# KMediaBridge license map

Copyright (c) 2026 Shusek

Starting with KMediaBridge 0.4.0, this repository is a mixed-license work:

- `api/**` and the first-party Kotlin implementation in `ffmpeg/**` are
  licensed under the KMediaBridge Internal Use Notice and Limited License in
  `LICENSES/LicenseRef-KMediaBridge-Internal.txt`.
- `native/**`, `ffmpeg-runtime-desktop/**`, `compliance/**`, `scripts/**`, and
  the build and release material needed to rebuild, inspect, replace, and
  redistribute the native runtime are licensed under LGPL-2.1-or-later. The
  complete text is in `LICENSES/LGPL-2.1-or-later.txt`.
- Third-party components retain their own licenses. See
  `THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md` and the manifests in `compliance/**`.

Unless an SPDX identifier or this map says otherwise, first-party files outside
`api/**` and `ffmpeg/**` are LGPL-2.1-or-later.

An SPDX identifier in a source file is authoritative for that file. Embedded
manifests and notices describe separately licensed runtime and third-party
components; embedding them does not change the license of the Kotlin module
that carries them.

Versions released through 0.3.0 remain available under the license conveyed
with those versions. This license map applies prospectively and does not
withdraw permissions already granted for an earlier copy.
